{"tid":301983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丁字褲火辣妹子現身北海岸 HE is so hot","createTime":"2017-06-29T04:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T05:15:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"416a29dd520e8d6a4f7f24a46ad0a5295e514d55","tid":301983,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"炎炎夏日是比基尼辣妹露出的戰場，今天早上10時許，民眾在北海岸的老梅風箏公園，發現一名身穿鮮黃色比基尼、丁字褲的辣妹，在海邊曬太陽，趕緊拍下火辣身影「好康道相報」，轉PO在臉書「就說北海岸」臉書專業，照片一出，引來網友熱議；事後才有網友出面說，「HE is so hot」，原來他是網紅「大奶酥」，是位愛穿女裝的大叔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來這名穿丁字褲的火辣身影，是網紅「大奶酥」，他在臉書自介文為「大家好，我是小bee，我是個愛穿女裝的大叔，因為又愛穿大假奶，所以自稱大奶酥」，網友將照片PO上臉書留言說，「夏日清晨，沙灘春光~He is so hot ?????」引來上百名網友熱議，紛紛要求說「跪求正面」，「&nbsp;哇～難得一見，超級涼快啊！」、「小心哦！會卡到陰！哈哈」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170629/640_5830692fde05b2d7e2c25131808628c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170629%2F640_5830692fde05b2d7e2c25131808628c9.jpg&h=79aa522a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f40f5cdd9817188e8432b6e13eea6e74bd9f8c4","tid":301983,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/125929_87d0f72367b05a80b4dbd033c8d2b8bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F125929_87d0f72367b05a80b4dbd033c8d2b8bc.jpg&h=4061b993&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34d28da9d65a9ff2baea0db8a53e83fab9923cd","tid":301983,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/125929_87d0f72367b05a80b4dbd033c8d2b8bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F125929_87d0f72367b05a80b4dbd033c8d2b8bc.jpg&h=4061b993